Description:
Prolux Advanced Semiconductors, registered in Hong Kong and operated in Beijing China, specialize in Gallium Nitride (GaN) and Gallium Arsenide (GaAs) semiconductors for LED, laser diode, HEMT, power devices and detectors. With numbers of world-leading professionals from Taiwan and Institute of Semiconductors, China Academy of Sciences, as well as cutting-edge equipments, we are confident to maintain technological advantages in our fields. 

    As a talent-driven and technology-driven company, Prolux Advanced Semiconductors consistently attach high importance to technological development and innovation and continuously keep a close eye on III-V semiconductors frontier. With integrated epitaxy, chip process and testing facilities, we currently provide series of high-quality and high-performance products for commercial customers and academic researchers:
    ·GaN LED wafers: Ultra-violet (380~410nm); high-brightness blue LED wafer (445~475nm) and high-brightness green LED wafer (505nm~530nm);
    ·GaAs LED wafers: High-brightness yellow wafer (580nm~595nm); high-brightness orange wafer (595nm~610nm); high-brightness red wafer (610~630nm); Wafer-bonding red wafer (610~630nm);
    ·AlGaN/GaN HEMT wafers: both sapphire-based and silicon-based;
    ·GaN substrate: free-standing GaN substrate;
    ·LD wafers: 808nm LD wafer;
    ·GaAs/InP wafer customization: customization services for rsearchers.

    We concentrate on performance upgrade and cost down for existing mature product lines and make full preparations for new expansions. Deep UV, GaN and SiC-based devices for power application and radio frequency are in our schedule.  

     We believe in semiconductor industry that significantly reshapes modern new life and do our best to deliver value to all our customers and users.

ShenZhen INFINITECH Technology Co.,Ltd Since in 2013 the headquarters in ShenZhen, in Hong Kong/Nan Jing/Shang Hai/BeiJing/TaiPei respectively with offices and branches;China's electronics industry one of the best solutions provider and value-added distribution enterprises;As wearable equipment markets around the world began to rise, the suitable technology take the lead and Ineda wear science and technology cooperation, as China's first agent to be a partner with Ineda complete scheme of autonomous technology;
To provide the world's most advanced intelligent wearable apparatus lowest power consumption of the SOC chip and application solutions.
We can provide customers with international leading apparel equipment solution, the industry the highest conversion efficiency of solar energy storage and power supply solutions, as well as digital power/representative/forward-looking products such as sensor;
At the same time, the ways and technology as the world's several famous multinational semiconductor companies in the greater China region important distributor, is also a important supplier of electronics manufacturing and research and development enterprises, products cover a wide range of industrial electronics, communications equipment, consumer electronics, automotive electronics, Internet, mobile phone application, etc.
With the remarkable demand creation ability and the core team of experienced, close to 55% of average annual compound growth rate and stable development, rapid growth of China's electronics industry one of the most advantages and the influence of the distribution enterprise.
